dct_description_sm: by J. Bartholomew, F. R. G. S. ; George Philip & Son, London & Liverpool.
Relief shown by hachures and spot heights.
5 bar scales in English Miles, Kilometres, Geographical Miles, Swedish Miles, and Norwegian Miles.
Includes references to Stifts (administrative jurisdictions) of Norway (distinguished on map by coloring).
Shows railways, various roads, waterways, most cities, small islands.
